<mxfile host="Electron" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) draw.io/29.6.1 Chrome/142.0.7444.265 Electron/39.8.0 Safari/537.36" version="29.6.1">
  <diagram name="Page-1" id="r_9ghK04LIl-eqNRj9zy">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1281" dy="626" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="ba-leZjCrm6MkJ4u5hA0-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Aim&lt;/b&gt;: Design a e-commerce system with following requirements:&lt;div&gt;1. User Login service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Search Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Product Catalog service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Cart Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.order status service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. check out service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimize the product searching and inventory stock management in real time.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="710" x="70" y="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ba-leZjCrm6MkJ4u5hA0-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Functional Requirements:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.User can able to login/register.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.User can able to search product.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. User can search the required object.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. easy to add required object to the cart and update.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. At end can make the payment of the cart.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. stock of the required product should be updated side by side.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Non Functional Requirements:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Availability &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; consistency:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The system should be more available as billion of users using the ecommerce website every single day.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Suppose, the website could afford the search time to be 50 to 100 ms(consistency) but cannot the system should be down for a particular period of time.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Latency:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;A user is able to search , update cart upto 20-50 ms.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. Scalability:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;The platform is able to handle demand of users on sale or big billion days.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. QPS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The system should be able to handle multiple queries at a single time. This means the latency should be low.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="340" width="590" x="70" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
